{"tid":2153204,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【濫用私刑】黑警圍毆市民","createTime":"2020-08-12T11:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T12:00:33.000Z","uid":365733,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a475f05105709fc3aa8d382589dc238f48d5076","tid":2153204,"uid":365733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T5yfC7B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT5yfC7B.jpg&h=24a89d54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bshTpNB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbshTpNB.jpg&h=52abc3db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚約十時許，於旺角朗豪戲院對出，一名的士司機與警員發生爭執，<span class=\"red\">其後被警方強行打開車門</span>，並把男子拉離司機座位，雙方一度口角。爭執期間，有警員突然粗暴地推跌該名男子。<br />\n<br />\n本台記者拍攝到在男子倒下後，有<span class=\"red\">警員用腳踢向該名男子的身體數下</span>。以下6張照片為事發經過。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112449543725160/posts/174988394137941/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112449543725160%2Fposts%2F174988394137941%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7XKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=ba05d816\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112449543725160/posts/174988394137941/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"5e6851a20f5f31924e0b7f77265710c7f8ba683f","tid":2153204,"uid":365733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:40:41.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5350bc0adfb679b07501dc450ccc80b50086fbb","tid":2153204,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1d9f6a2e0708c37699d3d8238a5f626cb62b9a","tid":2153204,"uid":365733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":